QuestData.Title: See What You've Done
QuestData.Description:
We have gathered what forces we can. I hope it is enough.
Within the ruins of our necropolis awaits one final challenge. The one leading the salvage effort calls herself Gorgantus.
To preserve all that remains to us, we must end her.
Lead the attack, and the Eyes will join you. We will reclaim our home.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: The head gutter for the House of Constructs.
QuestData.RewardText: I shall execute Akarek's will once more.
